var TYPECOL={robe:"#9c5d7c",jupe:"#c08552",top:"#5b7591",pantalon:"#5b7152",manteau:"#7a6a86",accessoire:"#bd8a3e",enfant:"#cf86a4"};
var TYPELBL={robe:"Robe",jupe:"Jupe",top:"Haut",pantalon:"Pantalon",manteau:"Veste/Manteau",accessoire:"Accessoire",enfant:"Enfant"};
$("patFType").addEventListener("change",renderPatList);$("patFLevel").addEventListener("change",renderPatList);
function renderPatList(){
  var ft=$("patFType").value,fl=$("patFLevel").value;var el=$("patList");var cards=[];
  state.patrons.forEach(function(p){if(ft!="tous"&&ft!="repere"&&p.type!=ft)return;if(fl!="tous")return;var ph=p.img?'<div class="ph" style="background-image:url(\''+(p.img.indexOf("data:")===0?p.img:esc(p.img))+'\')"></div>':'<div class="ph">&#9986; patron</div>';var src=p.url?'<a href="'+esc(p.url)+'" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ouvrir le patron &#8599;</a>':'';cards.push('<div class="insp">'+ph+'<div class="bd"><div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:6px;"><span class="tag typ">repéré'+(p.type?" · "+esc(p.type):"")+'</span><button class="x" onclick="delPattern('+p.id+')">&times;</button></div><h4>'+esc(p.title)+'</h4>'+(p.note?'<div class="muted" style="font-size:13px;">'+esc(p.note)+'</div>':'')+'<div style="margin-top:10px;display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:center;font-size:13px;flex-wrap:wrap;"><button class="btn ghost sm" onclick="patternReperToProjet('+p.id+')">&#8594; carnet</button>'+src+'</div></div></div>');});
  if(ft!="repere"){PATLIB.filter(function(p){return (ft=="tous"||p.type==ft)&&(fl=="tous"||p.level==fl);}).forEach(function(p){var col=TYPECOL[p.type]||"#9c5d7c";var cached=state.patImg&&state.patImg[p.url];var topStyle=cached?("background-image:url('"+esc(cached)+"');background-color:"+col+";background-size:cover;background-position:center;"):("background:"+col+";");cards.push('<div class="patcard"><div class="top" data-url="'+esc(p.url)+'" style="'+topStyle+'">'+(cached?"":esc(TYPELBL[p.type]||""))+'</div><div class="bd"><div style="font-weight:600;">'+esc(p.name)+'</div><div class="muted" style="font-size:13px;margin-bottom:6px;">'+esc(p.brand)+'</div><div style="margin-bottom:8px;"><span class="tag lvl">'+esc(p.level)+'</span></div><div class="muted" style="font-size:13px;min-height:38px;">'+esc(p.desc)+'</div><a class="btn sm" style="margin-top:10px;display:inline-block;color:#fff;text-decoration:none;" href="'+esc(p.url)+'" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Voir le patron &#8599;</a> <button class="btn ghost sm" onclick="patternToProjet('+"'"+jsq(p.name)+"','"+jsq(p.brand)+"'"+')">+ carnet</button></div></div>');});}
  if(!cards.length){el.innerHTML='<div class="empty" style="grid-column:1/-1;">'+(ft=="repere"?"Tu n'as pas encore de patron repéré. Colle un lien ci-dessus.":"Aucun patron pour ce filtre.")+'</div>';return;}
  el.innerHTML=cards.join("");lazyThumbs();
}
function lazyThumbs(){var nodes=[].slice.call(document.querySelectorAll('#patList .top[data-url]')).filter(function(n){return !n.style.backgroundImage;});var i=0;function nx(){if(i>=nodes.length)return;var n=nodes[i++];var u=n.getAttribute("data-url");if(state.patImg&&state.patImg[u]!==undefined){if(state.patImg[u]){n.style.backgroundImage="url('"+state.patImg[u]+"')";n.textContent="";}return nx();}fetchHtml(u).then(function(h){var m=metaFrom(h);state.patImg[u]=m.img||"";if(m.img){n.style.backgroundImage="url('"+m.img+"')";n.textContent="";}save();}).catch(function(){state.patImg[u]="";}).then(function(){setTimeout(nx,180);});}nx();}
function patternToProjet(name,brand){state.projets.unshift({id:uid(),name:name,piece:brand,diff:"Intermédiaire",stat:"envie",tissu:"",date:""});save();renderProjets();renderCarnetStats();toast("Patron ajouté au carnet");}

